# VirtualizedList (Momentum) — Momentum guidance (Cursor)

**VirtualizedList** extends **[List](./list.mdc)** with [TanStack Virtual](https://tanstack.com/virtual/latest) for **very long** row lists. **`virtualizerProps` is required:** at least **`count`**, **`estimateSize`**, and **`getItemKey`**. The app renders **visible** rows only; use **`onVirtualItemsChange`** so each **[ListItem](./listitem.mdc)** sets **`data-index`** to match **`virtualItems`**. **Do not** put top/bottom padding on the scroll container in CSS—use **`paddingStart`** and **`paddingEnd`** on **`virtualizerProps`**. If you use **gap** between items in CSS, mirror the pixel value in **`virtualizerProps.gap`**. **[Listheader](./listheader.mdc)** uses the **`list-header`** slot like **List**. **Events (React):** **`onScroll`**, **`onVirtualItemsChange`**. Set **`observeSizeChanges`** when row heights can change (uses **ResizeObserver**).

See also: [List](./list.mdc), [ListItem](./listitem.mdc).

Browse the [Momentum Components catalog](https://momentum.design/en/components/) for naming; Storybook documents props and examples. Reference: [Storybook — VirtualizedList / Docs](https://momentum.design/storybook-static/index.html?path=/docs/components-virtualizedlist-virtualizedlist--docs). Optional: [Example](https://momentum.design/storybook-static/index.html?path=/story/components-virtualizedlist-virtualizedlist--example).

---

## Import

Requires <ThemeProvider> and <IconProvider> ancestors. See setup.mdc.

```jsx
import { VirtualizedList, ListItem, Listheader } from "@momentum-design/components/dist/react";
```

---

## What it is

- **Stable** **`getItemKey`** is critical when data **mutates**—otherwise scroll and content **jitter** (JSDoc).  
- For **short** lists, **[List](./list.mdc)** is simpler; use **VirtualizedList** at **hundreds+** rows or when performance requires it.

---

## Example (shell — `virtualizerProps` required)

```jsx
import { VirtualizedList, ListItem } from "@momentum-design/components/dist/react";

function LongList() {
  return (
    <VirtualizedList
      virtualizerProps={{
        count: 1000,
        estimateSize: 56,
        getItemKey: (i) => String(i),
        paddingStart: 0,
        paddingEnd: 0,
        gap: 0,
      }}
      onVirtualItemsChange={() => {
        /* set data-index on visible rows; see JSDoc + Storybook */
      }}
    >
      {/* Render rows from virtualItems in your app — see Storybook */}
    </VirtualizedList>
  );
}
```

Follow **`onVirtualItemsChange`**, **`data-index`**, and height/gap rules in [Storybook — VirtualizedList / Example](https://momentum.design/storybook-static/index.html?path=/story/components-virtualizedlist-virtualizedlist--example).

