## Checklist for Cursor prototypes

- [ ] **`ThemeProvider`** + **`IconProvider`** when rows use **Icon** / avatars per [setup.mdc](../setup.mdc)  
- [ ] **`virtualizerProps`** includes **`count`**, **`estimateSize`**, **`getItemKey`**  
- [ ] **`gap`** in props matches CSS gap/margin between rows  
- [ ] Prefer plain **[List](./list.mdc)** for small static lists  

